snippet.title: [Download v1.0.4] Star Revenge 0 - Galaxy of Origins - Release Video
snippet.description:
Ah yes, after idk how many years, finally I made a hack that isn't a remake for once... yes, all new levels. 15 main courses, 2 side levels and 122 stars total.
This is around normal Star Revenge difficulty, so stars easier and gets harder at the end. Anyway, enjoy :3



Download: https://romhacking.com/hack/star-revenge-0---galaxy-of-origins


If there is anything wrong, feel free to let me know and blame Tomatobird8 while you are at it.



Music: Cadence of Hyrule - Gleeockenspiel | Ported to sm64 by RetroNika
